  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educating Afghans in Peace and Human Rights</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In April of 2012, AIL hosted an international conference on love and forgiveness featuring Afghan writers, poets, scholars and musicians. The purpose of this conference was to reintroduce the ancient, peaceful culture and values of Afghanistan to its people after years of war and strife. This conference was such a success that AIL has been asked to host workshops on the topic for Afghan students, whom AIL believes will be the catalyst that brings peace, justice and human rights to Afghanistan.</narrative>
  </description>
